    <item>
      <title>05 Functions - 01 Defining a Function</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/personal-site/docs/python/5functions/05-functions-01-defining-a-function/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 17:08:10 +0530</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/personal-site/docs/python/5functions/05-functions-01-defining-a-function/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Functions are named blocks of code designed to perform a specific task. When you want to execute a task defined in a function, you call the function responsible for it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>05 Functions - 02 Scope</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/personal-site/docs/python/5functions/05-functions-02-scope/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 17:08:40 +0530</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/personal-site/docs/python/5functions/05-functions-02-scope/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;assigning-functions-to-different-names&#34;&gt;Assigning Functions to Different Names&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A function can be assigned to another name, allowing it to be referenced differently.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;expressive-code&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;figure class=&#34;frame not-content&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;figcaption class=&#34;header&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/figcaption&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;# Assigning a function to a new name&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nf&#34;&gt;f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;b&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;c&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;):&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;g&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;f&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;# g is now another name for f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/figure&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This technique is useful for passing functions as arguments to other functions.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>05 Functions - 03 Arguments &amp; Parameters (1)</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/personal-site/docs/python/5functions/05-functions-03-arguments-parameters-1/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 19:58:34 +0530</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/personal-site/docs/python/5functions/05-functions-03-arguments-parameters-1/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Values are passed to functions similar to assigning values to a name.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;expressive-code&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;figure class=&#34;frame not-content&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;figcaption class=&#34;header&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/figcaption&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nf&#34;&gt;power&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;):&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;power&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;# Assigns values explicitly&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/figure&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Immutable values remain unchanged at the calling point, while mutable values can be modified.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
